    FlowerWall Hire 

    Our products are available to hire for your event. Based in Hertfordshire, we are a national company covering the whole of the UK, though delivery charges do apply. Choose your favourite wall, letter or floral centrepiece and get in touch for your personalised quote. We just need your date and venue details. We can always design a bespoke product for your special occasion. Just send us a message with your requirements!
